_:N8e712d888e16415497298386e41b11c0 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Jan is an experienced Transformation Director and Chief Information Officer, having worked for PZ Cussons (a multi-national FTSE 250 company) as a member of the executive leadership team.</p>\n\n<p>Jan was accountable for defining and ensuring the delivery of a strategic transformation programme, cybersecurity and digital technology across the UK, Africa, Asia and the Australia and New Zealand Banking Group (ANZ). </p>\n\n<p>She has also delivered large commercial and technology transformation programmes for Yodel, easyJet and KPMG.</p>\n\n<p>Prior to this, she was the chair of North West Shared Infrastructure Services and Chief Information Officer within the NHS; and worked for British Airways, including Head of IT and change programmes and member of the executive leadership team of Subsidiaries.</p>\n" .
